{"tid":1850952,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［罷工］搵唔到人頂算唔算理由","createTime":"2020-01-29T21:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T07:06:39.000Z","uid":266282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"464781ab917279513187c22c4be0943974082420","tid":1850952,"uid":266282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T21:37:50.000Z","msg":"話說我做PT，最快星期六開工<br />\n早兩日同老細講話我會罷工，就算唔係咩表態，都係我因為工作上會接觸到大陸人所以唔想麻煩<br />\n佢回覆支持我罷工，不過臨時臨急搵唔到個信得過嘅代替<br />\n仲話唔係想逼我唔罷工，但如果係咁隨意就話罷工，遲啲公司有啲高啲position嘅嘢都唔會敢比我做<br />\n咁係咪即係要脅我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e08dae1345ceff1d90d4cdf5e6113d4cf761b89","tid":1850952,"uid":31787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T21:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔算理由"},{"pid":"865bbd0a557dd939ce646dca946830eca49ba271","tid":1850952,"uid":331861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:06:39.000Z","msg":"就算成功三罷 都要留意執行方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1849793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1849793</a>"}]}